@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_danjnb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v0 = 0.84
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.22)) / v0)
    tmp = (tmp - ((v1 + 0.37 + v0 + 0.85) / (v2 + 0.74 - tmp + 0.86)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.21)) / 0.84)
    v0 = ((v0 / v0) / 0.51)
    v2 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.52 + tmp + 0.31) * (v2 + 0.29 + v1 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
